==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exporter
<hw>Ex*port"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who exports;
the person who sends goods or commodities to a foreign country, in the
way of commerce; -- opposed to <contr>importer</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

